headline: SolarWinds Appoints Tim Karaca as Chief Financial Officer
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, June 18, 2025--SolarWinds, a leading provider of simple, powerful, secure observability and IT management software, announced the appointment of Tim Karaca as its Senior Vice President, Chief Financial Officer effective June 16, 2025.
